  "text": ", represents the average departure of natural origins [CITATION_1] \u03b2 and 2 \u03b2 from the true value \u03b2 . But in practical situations it is hardly possible to get an idea about \u2206 . Consequently, an unbiased estimator of \u2206 is proposed, namely",
